OL,6,FPolice have named a father-of-seven as
OL,7,Fthe victim of a suspected murder in
OL,8,FCardiff.
OL,10,FColin Richards, 48, from Grangetown,
OL,11,Fdied in Ely on Sunday, 7 April.
OL,13,FEmergency services responded to
OL,14,Freports of an incident in the Heol-Y-
OL,15,FBerllan and Heol Trelai area of Caerau
OL,16,Fshortly before 11.30pm, and a murder
OL,17,Finvestigation was subsequently
OL,18,Flaunched.
