OL,6,FAn incident room has been set up at
OL,7,FCardiff Central Police Station and
OL,8,Fdetectives are appealing for anyone
OL,9,Fwith information to please come
OL,10,Fforward.
OL,12,FIn a tribute released via South Wales
OL,13,FPolice, Mr Richards' family said:
OL,14,F"Colin was a much-loved father,
OL,15,Fgrandfather, son, brother, uncle,
OL,16,Fcousin, and an all-round family man.
OL,18,F"He leaves behind seven children who
OL,19,Fwill miss him greatly as he was very
OL,20,Factive in their lives.
