OL,6,F"Though the loss is deep, the power of
OL,7,Flove and friendship will always stay
OL,8,Falive. He will always be in our minds
OL,9,Fand forever in our hearts."
OL,11,FThree women, two aged 43 and one aged
OL,12,F28, who were arrested on suspicion of
OL,13,Fmurder have been released under
OL,14,Finvestigation.
OL,16,FDetective Superintendent Darren
OL,17,FGeorge, of the force's major crime
OL,18,Fteam, said: "Extensive enquiries are
OL,19,Fcontinuing as we establish the tragic
OL,20,Fevents which took place on Sunday
OL,21,Fnight.
