OL,6,F"Our thoughts are with the family and
OL,7,Ffriends of Mr Colin Richards.
OL,9,F"Police cordons are still in place,
OL,10,Fand I would like to thank the
OL,11,Fcommunity for their continued support
OL,12,Fand understanding while we progress
OL,13,Fthe investigation.
OL,15,F"We are appealing for anyone who would
OL,16,Fhave been in the Heol y Berllan and
OL,17,FHeol Trelai area of Caerau between
OL,18,F11pm and midnight on Sunday night to
OL,19,Fplease come forward with information
OL,20,Fno matter how insignificant they may
OL,21,Ffeel it is."
